Air Lease Corporation host Second Quarter 2015 Earnings Conference Call
Air Lease Corporation will host a conference call on August 6, 2015 at 4:30 PM Eastern Time to discuss the Companyâ€™s financial results for the second quarter of 2015.
Investors can participate in the conference call by dialing (877) 280-2126 domestic or (678) 562-4234 international. The passcode for the call is 60908790.
The conference call will also be broadcast live through a link on the Investor Relations page of the Air Lease Corporation website.
